---
title: Szechuan Chicken Ramen Soup  with Dark Meat Chicken, Spinach & Peanuts
description: This hearty soup is ready to warm you from the inside out in just 15 minutes! You’ll sizzle up dark meat chicken with our spicy Szechuan blend of spices, simmer in a savory soy-infused broth, then add in quick-cooking ramen noodles. Toss in fresh spinach for pops of vibrant color, then sprinkle with crushed peanuts before serving for extra flavor and crunch.

